!bench/results/s9_residual_final_evidence/
!bench/results/s9_residual_final_evidence/README.md
!bench/results/s9_residual_final_evidence/summary.json
!bench/results/s9_residual_final_evidence/report.md
# S10c skill-injection A/B evidence (2026-04-16). Narrow allowlist:
# only the comparator markdown + the honest analysis note are tracked;
# the 8 per-seed run directories stay gitignored. First-try TS was
# INCONCLUSIVE (infra crash in yosys-jsonheader), resolved by S10f;
# second TS is the real GATE GREEN evidence.
!bench/results/s10c_20260416T183436Z_comparison.md
!bench/results/s10c_20260416T183436Z_analysis.md
!bench/results/s10c_20260416T185823Z_comparison.md
!bench/results/s10c_20260416T185823Z_analysis.md
# S10g LLM-sizing A/B — Miller OTA one-shot, first POSITIVE signal
# for skill injection (+10% Pass@1 abs over 10-seed pairs).
!bench/results/s10g_20260416T195409Z_comparison.md
!bench/results/s10g_20260416T195409Z_analysis.md
# S10h fazyrv A/B — digital skills on real RISC-V; NEUTRAL (no
# regression, no positive signal; same trajectory both arms).
!bench/results/s10h_20260416T204609Z_comparison.md
!bench/results/s10h_20260416T204609Z_analysis.md
